  "detailed_description": "Originally a jam game, <strong>Crown and Council</strong> is a casual strategy game of geopolitical drama. Conquer, expand, build and develop your kingdom, until all your foes are crushed!<br><br>Crown and Council relied on procedural generation for the 75 included maps. The generator is built into the game, and you can generate new maps on the fly.",
